  <summary date="2023-10-30T19:26:44Z" status="Introduced in House">Curbing Illicit Drug Threats Act

This bill requires the Government Accountability Office to study the effectiveness of federal drug surveillance systems, such as the Drug Overdose Surveillance and Epidemiology System of the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, in monitoring and addressing illicit drug use.</summary>
